Oops, sorry for the long delay, I didn't realized my chrome logged me out of github.
It seemed like the sanity check failed because of tensorflow's indentation width is 2 spaces instead of 4.
I have also fixed __ldg's backward compatibility error in Linux GPU test.
All the other checks seem to be aborted by unknown. Except the buildifier error in sanity check, which I am not really sure how to fix it.

body:
Oops, sorry for the long delay, I didn't realized my chrome logged me out of github.
It seemed like the sanity check failed because of tensorflow's indentation width is 2 spaces instead of 4.
I have also fixed __ldg's backward compatibility error in Linux GPU test.
All the other checks seem to be aborted by unknown. Except the buildifier error in sanity check, which I am not really sure how to fix it.
